<article class="node-58 node node-page view-mode-full" about="/content/about-aai-foresight" typeof="foaf:Document">

      <header>
                  <span property="dc:title" content="AAI Foresight Home Page" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span>
          </header>
  
  <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>The issues facing institutions are becoming increasingly complex and challenging. AAI Foresight identifies and tracks those issues, and provides strategic planning, organizational development, messaging, marketing, and technological assessment for a broad range of clients.</p>
<p>Timothy C. Mack, AAI Foresight’s founder and managing principal, has several decades of experience advising clients in such fields as manufacturing, healthcare, insurance, and energy. As well, he led the World Future Society from 2004 to 2014, then the world’s oldest and largest nonprofit, nonpartisan association devoted to studying forces shaping the future. In addition to his extensive writing in the public policy, marketing, and technology areas, he has spoken at numerous conferences and made television and radio appearances<br />
internationally.</p>
<p>Learn more or book Tim Mack for speaking engagements <a href="../content/tim-mack-founder" target="_&quot;blank&quot;">here</a>.</p>
<p><b>Contact:</b><br />
AAI Foresight<br />
1619 Main Street, #1172<br />
Freeland, WA 98249<br />
E-mail: <a href="mailto:tcmack333@gmail.com">tcmack333@gmail.com</a><br />
Voice/text: Telephone: 202-431-1652</p>
</div></div></div>
  
  
</article>
